{"tid":155684,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[A/I]Clash of Clan CoC新手clan, 召集新手及老手","createTime":"2017-03-14T08:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T12:53:17.000Z","uid":91424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8f069821a608d7c039e93108afbba749938297a","tid":155684,"uid":91424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T08:27:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">高登仔新手俱樂部 [HKG] </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">Search 「高登仔新手」就會搵到個clan  </span><br />\n主要培育新手，clan war其次<br />\n走輕鬆向<br />\n唔會chur住大家玩<br />\n有10本~8本捐兵比新手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單clan規:<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: green;\">申請入會時，請附帶一句中文或港式英文</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.捐兵比例1:4,即收4兵，請捐返最少1兵(6本或以下者，不受此規限)<br />\n3.逢周未(正式場)clan war 請出兵最少1場，不求成績，只求盡力<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: purple;\">weekday clan war是練習場，主要供大家練習打cw，及解成就。出唔出兵，點樣打，都無所謂，悉隨尊便。</span><br />\n5.請勿無故缺席2星期正式場，否則以死魚方式處理。<br />\n6.定期清理死魚，留返個位比有需要既朋友<br />\n7.請積極參與，活躍討論，定期上水，多作交流。<br />\n8.<span style=\"color: navy;\">雖然個名叫高登仔，但歡迎非高登仔/CD rom加入</span><br />\n9.<span style=\"color: red;\">本clan以人話(正體中文)為主，謝絕5p字，火星字及殘體字等，非人類語言</span><br />\n10. 已有whatsapp group,方便交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎加入coc大家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHappy gaming<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f98fc2b5b7786377dc4619e941bb1ab5e742b1","tid":155684,"uid":91424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T12:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更新左1game2玩"},{"pid":"522095edd77cfc7d687d82d6fc040f24af034ce8","tid":155684,"uid":91424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T12:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}